137
00:11:26.491 --> 00:11:28.292
Aku sudah bilang tidak!

138
00:11:28.292 --> 00:11:29.652
Tuan.

139
00:11:29.952 --> 00:11:31.322
Tidak./ Tolonglah.

140
00:11:31.322 --> 00:11:33.322
Aku bilang tidak!/ Ayo.

141
00:11:33.322 --> 00:11:35.692
